Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.56,1:23:22.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,我去扔垃圾了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.56,1:23:24.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,拜托了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.18,1:23:41.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.45,1:23:44.78,ASS,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.20,1:24:07.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,你不用这样啊
