Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.78,1:26:02.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,真的很大呢
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.19,1:26:05.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,那么来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.39,1:26:10.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.46,1:26:14.12,ASS,,0,0,0,,好棒啊
