Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.50,1:32:30.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,真的很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.31,1:32:33.90,ASS,,0,0,0,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.39,1:32:48.79,ASS,,0,0,0,,好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.39,1:32:51.72,ASS,,0,0,0,,肉棒很大呢
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.13,1:32:53.72,ASS,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.13,1:32:57.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,真的好爽啊
