Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.35,1:34:24.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,真的好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.29,1:34:29.95,ASS,,0,0,0,,不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.96,1:34:36.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,不行了呢
